    slug: 'beyond-words-protective-behaviours-non-verbal-early-years',
    title: 'Beyond Words: Adapting Protective Behaviours Curriculum for Non-Verbal & Limited-Verbal Children in Early Years',
    category: 'Child Safety',
    excerpt: 'Discover effective, inclusive strategies for adapting protective behaviours education for non-verbal and limited-verbal children in early years settings, fostering safety and autonomy.',
    metaDescription: 'Discover effective, inclusive strategies for adapting protective behaviours education for non-verbal and limited-verbal children in early years settings, fostering safety and autonomy.',
    readTime: 6,
    date: 'April 2026',
