    slug: 'early-consent-toddlers-preschoolers-body-autonomy-abuse-prevention',
    title: 'Building Early Foundations: Practical Age-Appropriate Consent Education for Toddlers and Preschoolers to Empower Body Autonomy and Prevent Abuse',
    category: 'Child Safety',
    excerpt: 'Discover practical, age-appropriate strategies for teaching toddlers and preschoolers body autonomy and consent. Empower your young child with vital skills to prevent abuse from an early age.',
    metaDescription: 'Discover practical, age-appropriate strategies for teaching toddlers and preschoolers body autonomy and consent. Empower your young child with vital skills to prevent abuse from an early age.',
